news.title: SIPCOT industrial park will be set up on 800 acres land in Cheyyur: Tamil Nadu CM
news.para: He laid foundation stones for five new projects valued at Rs 497.6 crore and provided government welfare assistance worth Rs 508.3 crore to 50,606 beneficiaries on the occasion.

news.title: Omaxe to invest Rs 600 crore in Faridabad’s retail project
news.para: The development is part of Omaxe World Street, 27 acre of which is already operational and has over 250 brands.

news.title: Jharkhand government plans for tax on lands being used for commercial purposes: Minister
news.para: He emphasised that the government's initiative aims to enhance transparency in land-related matters, which have a significant impact on the state's law and order situation.

news.title: UK's Persimmon to build more homes after 2024 profit beats estimates
news.para: The forecast comes as affordability remains a concern in Britain's housing sector. Interest rate cuts by the Bank of England are expected to provide some support, but there is uncertainty over the pace of further monetary easing and domestic growth.

news.title: Panaji smart city completes 42 projects
news.para: Minister of state in the ministry of housing and urban affairs, Tokhan Sahu, released the information in the Rajya Sabha.

news.title: Maharashtra government to seize properties of developers over Rs 172 crore MHADA dues
news.para: Transit camps are generally used as temporary accommodations for tenants of dilapidated cessed buildings or residents of such buildings that are undergoing repairs or redevelopment work.

news.title: Goa government informs HC of 46 underassessed fees cases by TCP department
news.para: Division bench of Justices M S Karnik and Nivedita Mehta is hearing a PIL alleging that the TCP underassessed fees for conversion under Section 17(2), causing a loss of crores of rupees to the exchequer.

news.title: Revenue minister orders demolition of unauthorised bungalows in Mumbai
news.para: The issue was raised by BJP MLC Vikrant Patil. Speaking in the council during Question Hour, Patil said gangs in cahoots with revenue and BMC officials were preparing bogus CRZ maps in Malad Madh island areas.

news.title: Starwood Capital set to acquire 79% stake in Spain’s Aedas Homes: Report
news.para: Rival U.S. fund Castlelake currently controls 79% in Aedas and is eager to exit the company, the newspaper reported last year.

news.title: Kajol buys commercial space in Mumbai’s Goregaon for Rs 28.78 crore
news.para: The deal registered on March 6 values the commercial space at Rs 65,940 per sq ft. The purchase reflects a trend among high-net-worth individuals and celebrities investing in commercial real estate for stable rental yields and long-term capital appreciation.

news.title: Housing sales in Gurugram cross Rs 1.07 lakh crore in 2024: Report
news.para: In Delhi-NCR overall, PropEquity said the sales of residential properties rose 63 per cent to Rs 1,53,000 crore in 2024 from Rs 94,143 crore in the preceding year.

news.title: Maharashtra's 2025-26 budget allocates funds for affordable housing and infrastructure
news.para: Several key infrastructure projects announced in the budget including the third airport to cater to the country’s financial capital Mumbai are expected to enhance real estate prospects in the state.

news.title: Wells Fargo sues JPMorgan over troubled $481 million real estate loan
news.para: The lawsuit pits the fourth-largest U.S. bank against the largest, with Wells Fargo accusing JPMorgan of turning a blind eye during due diligence in pursuit of millions of dollars in fees.

news.title: Andhra Pradesh cabinet sub-committee revises land allocation arrangements
news.para: The committee has decided to continue the policy initiated between 2014-19 for allotment of land to different institutions and private firms.

news.title: Rajasthan HC lifts status quo on sealing of 19 buildings in Walled City
news.para: The bench of Chief Justice M M Shrivastava and Justice Bhuvan Goyal said that a coordinate bench had previously ordered these buildings' sealing on Feb 25 and they cannot intervene in that order.

news.title: Delhi municipal council attaches seven properties over non-payment of tax
news.para: The council has prepared a list of 41 defaulting properties on KG Marg, including flats, offices and commercial establishments, which have not cleared their property tax dues.

news.title: Irregularities found in Raipur master plan to be probed: Jharkhand finance minister
news.para: Finance minister OP Choudhary acknowledged that complaints regarding the master plan were received and informed the House that a committee was constituted to investigate the matter.

news.title: Land circle rates in several districts of Uttar Pradesh set to be revised
news.para: A govt spokesperson said that the process has already been completed in 37 districts, but the work is now set to start in important districts as well.

news.title: Mumbai: BMC seizes properties of two builders over Rs 21 crore tax default
news.para: According to a BMC release, the civic body has started a crackdown on those defaulting on property tax payments by seizing and auctioning their properties.
